“If You’d Only Believe” 是由[[洛珊·西門|洛珊·西門]], [[比利·休斯_(美国)|比利·休斯]](Billie Hughes) 和 Jermaine Jackson 共同創作。這首歌收綠在 The Jacksons 的 “ The Jacksons’ 2300 Jackson Street”專輯裡並由製作人 Michael Omartian 監製。<ref>{{Citation|title=If You'd Only Believe by The Jacksons - Track Info {{!}} AllMusic|url=https://www.allmusic.com/song/if-youd-only-believe-mt0030269772|accessdate=2022-06-04|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=POP RECORDINGS|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/style/1989/05/21/pop-recordings/847a64f5-cb2a-409b-96df-52d2a2e3ffdf/|newspaper=Washington Post|date=1989-05-21|accessdate=2022-06-04|issn=0190-8286|language=en-US|first=Geoffrey|last=Himes}}</ref>

“If You’d Only Believe” 是電視節目“The Jackson Family Honors”的片尾曲。[[麥可·傑克遜|麥可·傑克遜]] (Michael Jackson) 在節目最後加入傑克森家族和其他特別來賓一起演唱 “If You’d Only Believe.” 特別來賓包括[[席琳·狄翁|席琳·狄翁]]、Bruce Hornsby、[[葛蕾蒂絲·奈特|葛蕾蒂絲·奈特]]、和 Dionne Warwick。<ref>{{Cite news|title=The Jackson Family Reunited, Sort Of|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1994/02/21/arts/the-jackson-family-reunited-sort-of.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=1994-02-21|accessdate=2022-06-04|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Bernard|last=Weinraub}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Jermaine Jackson Biography: Biography|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=71U3EAAAQBAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&pg=PA139&dq=%22Roxanne+Seeman%22++&hl=en|publisher=Publishroom|date=2021-07-07|isbn=979-10-236-2038-2|language=fr|first=B. A.|last=Duffour|title=Jermaine Jackson Biography}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=If You Only Believe - Celine Dion: The Power of The Music|url=http://www.powerofthemusic.com/t%20power%20of.html|access-date=2022-06-04|work=www.powerofthemusic.com}}</ref>

歌手 Randy Crawford 之後翻唱 “If You’d Only Believe” 並收錄在她在1991年由[[華納唱片|華納唱片]]發行的 Through The Eyes of Love 專輯。

